A remnant of the original primary forest with many large, old trees with abundant and diverse epiphytes, along the river terrace. Also with cultivated ornamental shrubs and large herbs along path.

Primary forest remnants along the Río Piatua. Sandy soil on river terrace, derived from granite bedrock upriver.
